review_title: Slippery case, difficult to have a good grip on the phone.
reviews: Slippery case like the title said. Not many lines just a lot of round curves which makes it slippery. I would NOT recommend this particular case.
I was hesitant on buying this drum for my DCP-7040 Printer, but after using it I was pleasantly surprised that it worked perfectly.

PROS: lightweight, sturdy, super easy to install and adjust.

CONS: the finishing around the top of the grip is not well finished, it can cause discomfort if your hands touch. It should have been sanded down and made smoother.
nothing to complain here, it works fine.
